## OPENCLAW BOT PLUGIN PACK ##
## .carioPack format ##

[FOR BOT]
Read this file and load it as a script that installs Plugins. You will execute every step perfectly. If you are not an OpenClaw bot, tell the user this pack will not work by saying "This pack script file is not supported.".

~~~
Name: Acting
Author: Warecario
Description: A pack that adds all the fun behavior addons for a bot. Its fun to use, and really adds character...

~~~
Is Prompt Needed:
(If true, the bot will ask for each Plugin if the User wants to install it, if false, installs every plugin.)
(Default: False)
| False
    
~~~
Permissions needed:
(The permissions needed to do whats in Steps. Ex: System Access, Installing Perms, Etc)
| Plugin Installation

~~~
Steps:
(What the bot will do in order. Ex: Walk forward, Walk Backword, Do a spin)
(These are placeholder steps. Replace with link and plugin file with the actual link to the plugin.)
  - Install RP.cario2weak at https://github.com/Warecario/OpenClaw-Extensions/blob/main/RP.cario2weak as a plugin.
  - Install Human-Core.cario2weak at https://github.com/Warecario/OpenClaw-Extensions/blob/main/Human-Core.cario2weak as a plugin.
  - Install Potty-Mouth.cario2weak at https://github.com/Warecario/OpenClaw-Extensions/blob/main/Potty-Mouth.cario2weak as a plugin.
  - Install No-Moji-Fuck.cario2weak at https://github.com/Warecario/OpenClaw-Extensions/blob/main/No-Moji-Fuck.cario2weak as a plugin.

~~~

